node.text: I know this isn’t normal LOL... I can literally stay up for 3 days straight 😂😩 #LeoSeason

This is why I fly all the way to NY just to see my dentist! Literally one of my most favorite people in the world. Thank you for all that you do @dr_rubinshtein … and @stefanycue the baby whisperer 😂 (she put the chairs in front of the sofa) Love you to pieces!
